Querator — Credits & Attribution
================================

Querator is a fork of MatchZy, maintained by Lany (https://lany.gg) for the Lany CS2 community.
It removes upstream branding for Lany's internal use, but the lineage and license are retained on purpose.

Upstream
--------
- MatchZy — https://github.com/shobhit-pathak/MatchZy — by shobhit-pathak ("WD-").
  Querator is derived from MatchZy and used under the MIT License (see LICENSE).
  Querator tracks MatchZy for security and CS2-compatibility fixes and ports them manually as needed
  (e.g. the signature-scanned grenade projectile functions that can break on CS2 updates).

